<h2 style="margin:18px 0px 9px;padding:0px 0px 10px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:500;line-height:1.1;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:15px;vertical-align:baseline;letter-spacing:1px;text-align:center;color:#6a6a6a;background:none;">Witamy w sklepie internetowym Lumina Deco!</h2>
<div class="rte" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:18px;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;background:#ffffff none repeat scroll 0px 0px;color:#202020;">
